ine 行動升級 (幫推)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497453</a>"},{"pid":"09d93ab1010af6dcdfadd112f95fb9398620bccf","tid":1497792,"uid":45830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"條柒頭真係柒足好多年"},{"pid":"532277649f82147b50066a68171a27eb4d7d38e3","tid":1497792,"uid":133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dca5aecfc5657e597fe2e7361392e6a51d2ca3c8","tid":1497792,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"陸頌雄大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170818/photo/0818-00176-113b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170818%2Fphoto%2F0818-00176-113b1.jpg&h=6cb54935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎左P牌未?"},{"pid":"6e034fae6d26791debadafadb6aa6c05e2a13037","tid":1497792,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5046f3dfce75be01bda8ded3a667cec3cbd40308","tid":1497792,"uid":275901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:34:25.000Z","msg":"工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/29510953_608192962853777_2064288947012920306_n.png?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQlbfjlL3pH-x0qFIk1Xe2GuI2f_ztxnf9kkmthGLOU71pAQnMfYTbsCEaCJiqrCGfY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=d0d1cebc65f3fb8922e98b8436244060&amp;oe=5E0BCCB9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F29510953_608192962853777_2064288947012920306_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQlbfjl